#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Māghasutta "
msgstr "3. With Māgha "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.47, pts2ed1.106, sc1
msgctxt "sn2.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.3:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho māgho devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "Then, late at night, the glorious god Māgha, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "

msgctxt "sn2.3:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho māgho devaputto bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "and addressed the Buddha in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsu chetvā sukhaṃ seti, "
msgstr "“When what is incinerated do you sleep at ease? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.2"
msgid "kiṃsu chetvā na socati; "
msgstr "When what is incinerated is there no sorrow? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.3"
msgid "Kissassu ekadhammassa, "
msgstr "What is the one thing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.4"
msgid "vadhaṃ rocesi gotamā”ti. "
msgstr "whose killing you approve?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.1"
msgid "“Kodhaṃ chetvā sukhaṃ seti, "
msgstr "“When anger’s incinerated you sleep at ease. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.2"
msgid "kodhaṃ chetvā na socati; "
msgstr "When anger’s incinerated there is no sorrow. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.3"
msgid "Kodhassa visamūlassa, "
msgstr "Vatrabhū, anger has a poisoned root, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.4"
msgid "madhuraggassa vatrabhū; "
msgstr "and a honey tip. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.5"
msgid "Vadhaṃ ariyā pasaṃsanti, "
msgstr "The noble ones praise the slaying of anger, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.6"
msgid "tañhi chetvā na socatī”ti. "
msgstr "for when it’s incinerated there is no sorrow.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
